  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class PersonPicker
extends KSJInternalFrame
    The PersonPicker is a window that displays a menu of Individuals. When one person is selected, their fields are displayed to confirm it is the right one. When the User clicks the "Choose" button, the Individual selected is added to the appropriate field(s) of the editor which launched this picker.

    It is an extension of KSJInternalFrame so it will appear in the View menu.
